Package pathfind

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ISearchAlgorithm
    The Interface that helps differentiate the different types of path finding algorithms.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AStar
    The Class manages the AStar path algorithm and primarily finds the path from a location.
    AStarNode
    AStarNode.java Nodes that have costs and neighbors for a-star calculations
    BreadthFirst
    The Class manages the Breadth First path algorithm and primarily finds the path from a location.
    DepthFirst
    The Class manages the Depth First path algorithm and primarily finds the path from a location.
    Map
    This abstract Class deals with the Map and related methods.
    Map2D
    Class that deals with the 2D version of the map and related methods.
    Map3D
    Class that deals with the 3D version of the map and related methods.
    Path
    Path.java Holds path information from AStar and calculates text directions.
    Pathfinder
    Pathfinder.java Loads from database and calculates the fastest path between given nodes.
    QRCode
    This class deals with the QR code image and methods relating to it.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    NoPathFoundException  
    NoPathGeneratedException
